g src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">衛詩</span>（英文名：<span style=\"color: teal;\">Jill M. Vidal</span>，1982年4月13日－），香港女歌手，中韓菲混血兒，衛蘭的孿生妹妹。2006年至今已經推出了一張大碟《Hit Me》和一張EP《Diamond Love》，並在2008年8月8日推出一張新曲+精選《Jillympics》。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/37886242_1044915859005256_2022873345229324288_o.jpg?_nc_cat=0&amp;oh=d5c47097f35f427d386a23455001d8b6&amp;oe=5C0B953A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F37886242_1044915859005256_2022873345229324288_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D0%26oh%3Dd5c47097f35f427d386a23455001d8b6%26oe%3D5C0B953A&h=785653bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">人 偶爾要放懷排排坐 為活著慶賀</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">衛詩最新動態 </span></span></ins></strong><br />\n衛詩ig : <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/jillvidal/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fjillvidal%2F&d=ZoWAdkHkhVIKPu%2BUHwq9OTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=2cf5e4e9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/jillvidal/</a><br />\n衛詩官方fb: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/JillVidalOfficial/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FJillVidalOfficial%2F&d=ZoWAdkHkhVIKPu%2BUHwq9OTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=4fa96420\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/JillVidalOfficial/</a><br />\n衛詩官方youtube 頻道 : <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCfdaxOuYXT00i2q_b6pWg8Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCfdaxOuYXT00i2q_b6pWg8Q&d=ZoWAdkHkhVIKPu%2BUHwq9OTQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=306c9557\" t